oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Performance - Becky Buller Band - 2016-11-19
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Performance by the Becky Buller Band as part of the Bluegrass and Beyond program from the Ford Theater at the Country Music Hall of Fame and Museum on November 19, 2016. Fourth performance of four. Presented by the Crump family and Cotton Music. Honoring George A. and Marjorie S. Crump.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Becky Buller band;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dcterms:tableOfContents: Performance includes; Nothin' To You -- I Prayed For You -- Keep The Customer Satisfied -- Heart Of The House -- Unidentified Song [possibly Shame On Me (vocal by Daniel Hardin)] -- John D Champion -- Phoenix Arise -- Girl In The Blue Velvet Band (Dan Boner) -- Why Don't You Just Say Goodbye -- Cabin Of Death (Ned Luberecki) -- Didn't Die -- Southern Flavor -- Make Us To Shine.
